reviews.reviewTitle: Stable DDR4 ram with nice RGB
reviews.reviewText: Works great in my z690 system. Using 2 of these kits for 128GB for software development. Don't need to OC as I need stability...running at advertised speed with all 4 sticks installed. Great deal for what I have.

reviews.reviewTitle: Worked perfectly after I updated my BIOS
reviews.reviewText: Works perfectly. Fast and looks great.If you're running Ryzen I recommend making sure you're running the latest BIOS. Worked fine with a B550 Gigabyte motherboard.

reviews.reviewTitle: Seems to work well at advertised speeds
reviews.reviewText: Not much headroom for over clocking if you care about that. They definitely look nice and work well.
